com.bmd.android.collection.filter

Interface SimpleArrayMapFilterBuilder<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The entry key type.
    V - The entry value type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    FilterBuilder<SimpleArrayMapIterable<K,V>,SimpleArrayMapEntry<K,V>>

    public interface SimpleArrayMapFilterBuilder<K,V>
extends FilterBuilder<SimpleArrayMapIterable<K,V>,SimpleArrayMapEntry<K,V>>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SimpleArrayMapEntry elements.
